Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports: taxlist (>= 0.3.0)
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Description: 
    A collection of functions used to format taxonomic names in Markdown
    documents. Those functions work with data structured according to
    Alvarez and Luebert (2018) <doi:10.3897/bdj.6.e23635>.
